    public class FlexFileSet
extends org.apache.tools.ant.types.FileSet
implements IOptionSource
    Adds support for setting Flex configuration options using Ant FileSets. For example: <library-path dir="${FLEX_HOME}/libs" includes="flex.swc" append="true"/>
